title: Gorillaz - The Singles Collection 2001 - 2011 (Full Album)
description: The Singles Collection: 2001--2011 is a compilation album released by British virtual band Gorillaz on 25 November 2011. The album is a collection of the group's singles released between 2001 and 2011. The album is available in four different editions: standard, deluxe, 12" vinyl and 7" single box set.
